<!-- =================== 快速上手 =================== -->
<div class="section" id="quickstart">
<h1>快速上手</h1>
<h2>安装</h2>
<pre><code>&lt;script src="spark.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>

<h2>Hello World</h2>
<pre><code>Spark.Page({
  style: "padding: 24px;",
  child: [
    Spark.Text("Hello Spark.js!", {
      style: "font-size: 24px; color: #4B95FF; font-weight: bold;"
    }),
    Spark.Button("点击我", {
      style: "margin-top: 12px;",
      onClick: function () { alert("Hello!"); }
    })
  ]
});</code></pre>

<h2>核心概念</h2>
<h3>声明式组件</h3>
<p>所有 UI 都是 JavaScript 函数调用的返回值。使用 <code>child</code> 属性组合嵌套组件，类似 Flutter 的 Widget 树。</p>
<pre><code>var card = Spark.Box({
  style: "padding: 16px; border: 1px solid #eee;",
  child: [
    Spark.Text("标题", { style: "font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;" }),
    Spark.Text("这是一段描述文字")
  ]
});</code></pre>

<h3>响应式属性</h3>
<p>部分组件属性支持响应式更新：直接赋值时 DOM 自动更新。</p>
<pre><code>var title = Spark.Text("旧标题");
title.text = "新标题"; // DOM 自动更新</code></pre>

<h3>事件绑定</h3>
<pre><code>Spark.Box({
  style: "padding: 12px; cursor: pointer;",
  onClick: function () { console.log("clicked!"); },
  onMouseOver: function () { this.style = "background:#f0f0f0;"; },
  onMouseOut: function () { this.style = "background:transparent;"; }
});</code></pre>

<h3>样式管理</h3>
<pre><code>Spark.Css({
  ".title": "font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:#333;",
  ".card": "padding:16px; border-radius:8px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"
});</code></pre>

<h2>页面路由</h2>
<pre><code>Spark.router({
  el: "#app",
  module: { "/": HomeComponent, "/about": AboutComponent },
  cache: true
});</code></pre>
</div>

<!-- =================== 核心 API =================== -->
<div class="section" id="api">
<h1>核心 API</h1>

<h2>全局方法</h2>
<div class="prop-list">
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.Page(p)</span><span class="prop-desc">创建页面根容器</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.Css(p)</span><span class="prop-desc">定义全局 CSS 样式映射</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.router(p)</span><span class="prop-desc">启动路由 — { el, module, cache }</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.append(target, children)</span><span class="prop-desc">向父容器追加子组件</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.prepend(target, children)</span><span class="prop-desc">向父容器头部插入子组件</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.remove(target, child)</span><span class="prop-desc">移除子组件</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.getWidget(address)</span><span class="prop-desc">根据 vdom 地址获取组件</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.onReady(fn)</span><span class="prop-desc">DOM 加载完成后执行</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.destroy()</span><span class="prop-desc">销毁所有缓存和组件</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">Spark.axios</span><span class="prop-desc">内置 HTTP 请求库</span></div>
</div>

<h2>通用参数</h2>
<p>几乎所有组件都接受以下通用参数：</p>
<div class="prop-list">
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">style</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-desc">CSS 内联样式</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">class</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-desc">CSS 类名（引用 Spark.Css 定义）</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">child</span><span class="prop-type">Array</span><span class="prop-desc">子组件数组</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">onClick</span><span class="prop-type">Function</span><span class="prop-desc">点击事件</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">onMouseOver</span><span class="prop-type">Function</span><span class="prop-desc">鼠标移入</span></div>
  <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">onMouseOut</span><span class="prop-type">Function</span><span class="prop-desc">鼠标移出</span></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- =================== Text 文本 =================== -->
<div class="section" id="comp-text">
<div class="comp-layout">
  <div class="comp-doc">
    <h1>Text 文本 <span class="tag tag-base">Base</span></h1>
    <p>最基础的文本显示组件。支持响应式 <code>text</code> 属性更新。</p>
    <h2>基础用法</h2>
    <pre><code>var title = Spark.Text("Hello World", {
  style: "font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #333;"
});

// 响应式更新
title.text = "新文本内容";</code></pre>
    <h2>API</h2>
    <div class="prop-list">
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">第 1 参数</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">""</span><span class="prop-desc">显示文本</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">style</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">-</span><span class="prop-desc">CSS 内联样式</span></div>
    </div>
    <h3>响应式属性</h3>
    <div class="prop-list">
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">text</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-desc">设置/获取文本内容，自动更新 DOM</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">style</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-desc">设置/获取样式，自动更新 DOM</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="comp-demo">
    <div class="demo-card">
      <div class="demo-card-title">效果预览</div>
      <div class="demo-card-body">
        <span style="font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;color:#333;">Hello World</span>
        <span style="font-size:16px;color:var(--primary);">Spark.js 文本组件</span>
        <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-sec);">支持响应式更新</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- =================== Button 按钮 =================== -->
<div class="section" id="comp-button">
<div class="comp-layout">
  <div class="comp-doc">
    <h1>Button 按钮 <span class="tag tag-base">Base</span></h1>
    <p>按钮组件，默认带有发光蓝色主题样式。</p>
    <h2>基础用法</h2>
    <pre><code>Spark.Button("默认按钮", {
  onClick: function () { alert("Button clicked!"); }
});

Spark.Button("危险按钮", {
  style: "background-color: #ff4d4f; border-color: #ff4d4f;",
  onClick: function () { console.log("danger!"); }
});</code></pre>
    <h2>API</h2>
    <div class="prop-list">
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">第 1 参数</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">""</span><span class="prop-desc">按钮文字</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">style</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">蓝色主题</span><span class="prop-desc">CSS 内联样式</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">onClick</span><span class="prop-type">Function</span><span class="prop-default">-</span><span class="prop-desc">点击回调</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="comp-demo">
    <div class="demo-card">
      <div class="demo-card-title">效果预览</div>
      <div class="demo-card-body">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <span class="d-btn">默认按钮</span>
          <span class="d-btn d-btn-outline">边框按钮</span>
          <span class="d-btn d-btn-danger">危险按钮</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;margin-top:4px">
          <span class="d-btn d-btn-sm">小号按钮</span>
          <span class="d-btn" style="opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed">禁用状态</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- =================== Link 链接 =================== -->
<div class="section" id="comp-link">
<div class="comp-layout">
  <div class="comp-doc">
    <h1>Link 链接 <span class="tag tag-base">Base</span></h1>
    <p>超链接组件，渲染为 <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> 标签。</p>
    <h2>基础用法</h2>
    <pre><code>Spark.Link("访问首页", {
  href: "/",
  target: "_blank",
  style: "color: #4B95FF;"
});</code></pre>
    <h2>API</h2>
    <div class="prop-list">
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">第 1 参数</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">""</span><span class="prop-desc">链接文字</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">href</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">"javascript:;"</span><span class="prop-desc">目标URL</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">target</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">-</span><span class="prop-desc">打开方式 (_blank/_self)</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="comp-demo">
    <div class="demo-card">
      <div class="demo-card-title">效果预览</div>
      <div class="demo-card-body">
        <a href="javascript:;" style="color:var(--primary);font-size:14px;">访问首页</a>
        <a href="javascript:;" style="color:var(--primary);font-size:14px;">查看文档 →</a>
        <a href="javascript:;" style="color:#ff4d4f;font-size:14px;">危险操作链接</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- =================== Image 图片 =================== -->
<div class="section" id="comp-image">
<div class="comp-layout">
  <div class="comp-doc">
    <h1>Image 图片 <span class="tag tag-base">Base</span></h1>
    <p>图片组件，支持响应式 <code>src</code> 属性。</p>
    <h2>基础用法</h2>
    <pre><code>var img = Spark.Image("https://example.com/photo.jpg", {
  style: "width: 200px; border-radius: 8px;"
});
img.src = "https://example.com/another.jpg";</code></pre>
    <h2>API</h2>
    <div class="prop-list">
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">第 1 参数</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">""</span><span class="prop-desc">图片 URL</span></div>
      <div class="prop-item"><span class="prop-name">style</span><span class="prop-type">String</span><span class="prop-default">-</span><span class="prop-desc">CSS 内联样式</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="comp-demo">
    <div class="demo-card">
      <div class="demo-card-title">效果预览</div>
      <div class="demo-card-body center">
        <div style="width:140px;height:100px;border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:13px;">Image</div>
        <div style="width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f093fb,#f5576c);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:11px;">圆形</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
